article.linkText: Hargress scores 21 as UC Riverside beats Cal State Fullerton 81-73
article.story: FULLERTON, Calif. -- — Barrington Hargress had 21 points in UC Riverside's 81-73 victory over Cal State Fullerton on Thursday night. Hargress also contributed eight rebounds and six assists for the Highlanders (11-15, 6-8 Big West Conference). Nate Pickens hit three 3-pointers and scored 19. Kaleb Smith pitched in with 10 points, while adding nine rebounds. Tory San Antonio finished with 14 points for the Titans (11-14, 4-9). Dominic Brewton added 13 points. Grayson Carper had 12 points and 10 rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
